data.frame(theta = tr_dat)%>%
    rownames_to_column('label') %>%
    left_join(sp_colors) %>%

library(sf)
gridz <- st_make_grid(occ_sf, cellsize = 1.5,
                      what = 'polygons',square = F, 
                      crs = st_crs(occ_sf)) %>%
  st_as_sf() %>%
  rownames_to_column('ID') 


gridz %>%
  st_join(occ_sf) %>%
  st_drop_geometry() %>%
  na.omit() %>%
  mutate(shift = if_else(label %in% sp_shift_temp, 'Niche Shift in Temperature', 'Conserved Niche')) %>%
  group_by(ID, shift) %>%
  mutate(richness = n_distinct(sp),
            records = n()) %>%
  inner_join(gridz, .) %>%
  filter(records >0) %>%
  mutate(ID = as.numeric(ID))-> hex_rich
Joining with `by = join_by(ID)`

data("World")
tmap_mode('plot')
tmap mode set to plotting
hillshade <- rast('D:/R_spatial/data/raster/MSR_50M/MSR_50M/MSR_50M.tif') %>% 
  crop(vect(World), mask = T ) 


hex_rich %>%
select(ID, shift, richness) %>% 
  distinct() ->shift_sf


tm_shape(hillshade, bbox = st_bbox(shift_sf)) +
  tm_raster(palette = '-Greys',style = 'cont',
            contrast = c(0.6,1), legend.show = F) +
tm_shape(shift_sf) +
  tm_fill('richness', palette = '-inferno',
          contrast = c(0.1,1), alpha = 0.7,
          title = c('(A)\nSpecies richness', '(B)\nSpecies richness')) + 
  tm_facets('shift', ncol = 2) +
    tm_shape(World) +
  tm_borders('grey50', alpha = 0.5) +
